definitions.name: Evelyn
definitions.description:
Have you the need to burn a hole or two in your wallet, paired with an inability to signal for lane changes? This flashy coupe lets you flaunt your wealth whilst effortlessly accommodating the swiftest of one-lane-over maneuvers.
All-wheel drive
ABS equipped
TCS equipped
